Thank you for downloading Veera Yugam Demo!

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS:
1. Right-click VeeraYugam_Demo_Setup.exe
2. Select "Run as administrator"
3. Follow the installation wizard
4. Launch from Start Menu or Desktop shortcut

MINIMUM SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS:
- OS: Windows 10/11 (64-bit)
- CPU: Intel Core i5-8400 / AMD Ryzen 5 2600
- RAM: 8GB (16GB recommended)
- GPU: NVIDIA GTX 1060 6GB / AMD RX 580 8GB
- DirectX: Version 12
- Storage: 5GB available space

DEMO INCLUDES:
- Chola Capital City (Chapter 1)
- Character creation: Veeran
- 3 main story missions
- Basic combat system
- 5 weapon types
- Horse riding tutorial
- Full keyboard + gamepad support

CONTROLS:
W/A/S/D - Movement      SPACE - Jump/Dodge
LMB - Attack            RMB - Block/Aim
E - Interact            TAB - Inventory
F - Special Ability     ESC - Pause Menu

